+## Overview
+
+The 30 orders generated total revenue of $7,154.44. The median order value was $204.95.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget led revenue at $2,392.00, followed by Widget at $2,118.94. Doohickey produced $1,513.00 and Sprocket $1,130.50.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North ranked first with $2,176.35. East earned $1,830.79, South $1,732.48, and West $1,414.82.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget sales, the highest-revenue product at $2,392.00.
+- Study North's sales mix and apply successful tactics in West, the lowest-revenue region.
+- Seek Sprocket growth opportunities; it generated the least product revenue at $1,130.50.
